headline: Wall Street Analysts Think Qualcomm (QCOM) Could Surge 28.45%: Read This Before Placing a Bet
summary: The average of price targets set by Wall Street analysts indicates a potential upside of 28.5% in Qualcomm (QCOM). While the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric is questionable, the positive trend in earnings estimate revisions might translate into an upside in the stock.
